<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1381</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shén a shén a yòu shì yī gè zǎo chén, wǒ yào xiàng nǐ xiàn shàng gǎn ēn de xīn,
 yīn wèi zǎo chén nǐ bì tīng wǒ de shēng yīn, jiù shì chēng sòng jìng bài qí dǎo de shēng yīn,
 zǎo chén wǒ bì xiàng nǐ chén míng wǒ de xīn yì, wǒ bì xiàng nǐ chǎng kāi wǒ de xīn,
 bìng yào jǐng xǐng, nǐ lái guāng zhào zhǐ yǐn, shén a wǒ yào xiàn shàng gǎn ēn de xīn.
 shén a wǒ yào xiàn shàng gǎn ēn de xīn.</lyrics>
<title>shén a yòu shì yī gè zǎo chén 迦南1381</title>
</song>